### Articles - Create
POST {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"title": "使用 .NET 8 构建新博客",
	"content": "<p>欢迎使用全新的 .NET 8 后端。</p>",
	"contentMarkdown": "# 欢迎\n这是 Markdown 版本的内容。",
	"coverImage": "https://example.com/images/dotnet8.jpg",
	"category": "Study"
}

### Articles - List All
GET {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles
Accept: application/json

### Articles - Summary List
GET {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles?summary=true
Accept: application/json

### Articles - Paginated List
GET {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles?page=1&limit=5
Accept: application/json

### Articles - Featured
GET {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles/featured?limit=3
Accept: application/json

### Articles - Get By Id
@articleId = 11
GET {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles/{{articleId}}
Accept: application/json

### Articles - Update
PUT {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles/{{articleId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"title": "更新后的 .NET 8 博客",
	"category": "Work"
}

### Articles - Delete
DELETE {{BlogApi_HostAddress}}/articles/{{articleId}}

